Cron entries:

```
# 05:00 — Paperless export to TrueNAS
0 5 * * * /bin/bash /usr/local/bin/backup-paperless.sh >> /var/log/paperless-backup.log 2>&1

# 05:30 — Immich incremental backup to TrueNAS
30 5 * * * /bin/bash /usr/local/bin/backup-immich.sh >> /var/log/immich-backup.log 2>&1

# 06:30 — Upload TrueNAS exports to pCloud (logs handled internally by script)
30 6 * * * /bin/bash /usr/local/bin/pcloud-export-backup.sh

# 07:00 — Daily integrity check of pCloud against TrueNAS
0 7 * * * /bin/bash /usr/local/bin/pcloud-integrity-check.sh
```

> **Note:** The rclone scripts manage their own log files internally via `--log-file`. No cron redirection is needed for those jobs — avoid it to prevent duplicate log entries.

