## 21. Final Backup Layers

| Layer | Description |
|---|---|
| ZFS snapshots | protects dataset from deletion and corruption |
| TrueNAS storage | primary backup repository |
| pCloud | off-site disaster recovery |
| PBS backups | full VM restore |

